    <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Key Contributions</h2>

    <!-- FIX 1 + 2 -->
    <p class="intro-text reveal">
      We evaluate SenseGuard in Connected and Autonomous Vehicles (CAVs)—a demanding setting with massive sensor data, strict real-time constraints, and safety-critical decisions. Solutions that succeed here generalize naturally to broader robotic systems.
    </p>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="contribution-grid reveal">

